Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements

Class ValidValueElement

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements.ValidValueElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
MetadataElement
public class ValidValueElement extends Object implements MetadataElement
ValidValueElement contains the properties and header for a valid value definition or set entity retrieved from the metadata repository.
